<ab facs="#facs_246_r2l3">vnd <expan>ſelıgma<ex>n</ex>s</expan> ſeıns <expan>brud<ex>er</ex>s</expan> der Juden <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc Alſo <expan>ſend<ex>en</ex></expan> wır ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_246_r2l4"><expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>Burkart<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>Reıkarcʒhof<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> dem wır <expan>befolhe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_246_r2l5"><expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> mıt eẅ <expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒureden Vnd <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mıt fleıſſ vvas </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_246_r2l6"><expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> in den <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> ſachen ʒu dıſem mal von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_246_r2l7">an eẅ werbe . Daʒ Jr Jm das <expan>gencʒl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>gelawbe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd gütlıch <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_246_r2l8">von eẅ <expan>fertıg<ex>en</ex></expan> wellet . als etc / Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_246_r2l9"><expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> vȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nicam</expan> <expan>Palma<ex>rum</ex></expan> </ab>
