</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_246" id="122r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Dieth<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Lantschad<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>vicztu<ex>m</ex></expan> zu
                                <expan>Aschaffemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> vicztum, als ir uns nehst
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von Yosep Püczels und
                                <expan>Seligma<ex>n</ex>s</expan> seins
                            <expan>brud<ex>er</ex>s</expan> der juden <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        etc., also <expan>send<ex>en</ex></expan> wir zu
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>Burkart<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Reikarczhof<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, dem wir <expan>befolhe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, mit ew <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> zu
                        reden, und <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr
                            <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit fleiss, was
                                <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> in den <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
                        sachen zu disem mal von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> an ew werbe, daz ir im das
                                <expan>genczl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>gelawbe<ex>n</ex></expan> und gütlich <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
                        von ew <expan>fertig<ex>en</ex></expan> wellet. Als etc. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nicam</expan>
<expan>palma<ex>rum</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
